This roll bundles the mono C# compiler and runtime.  To install, execute these
instructions on a Rocks development machine (e.g., a frontend), starting in
this directory:

% make
% rocks add roll *.iso
% rocks enable roll mono
% cd /export/rocks/install
% rocks create distro
% rocks run roll mono | bash

In addition to the software itself, the roll installs mono environment module
files in /opt/modulefiles/compilers/beast.
